PrecisAcceptance of an Instrument wherein the SKWAY BAND (a) revokes a 1954 Surrender affecting the whole of Skway Indian Reserve No. 5, in British Columbia, and (b) surrenders, for a term of 20 years, some 7.11 hectares of that same reserve, for the purpose of leasing them to third parties for commercial and industrial uses.
